      "content": "are you sure though?? it doesn't really feel like an emergency, it's just a localized ache. plus the clinic is like a 40 min drive and im literally a mess right now. i feel like if i just take a couple of the codeine i'll be fine by morning and it'll just be a weird cramp. wouldn't it be better to just manage the pain for a few hours so i can rest? if i go now i'll just be sitting in an er waiting room for 6 hours for nothing.",
